  constructor() {
    this.shortIndexes = {};

  static cleanSearchText(text) {

    result = result.replace(badCharsRe, ' ').replace(trimRe, '');

    if (!searchText.length) {

    this.fullTexts[id] = searchText;
    searchText.split(' ').forEach(searchWord => {
      const len = Math.min(searchWord.length, 3);
      let wordPart;
      let i;

      for (i = 1; i <= len; i += 1) {
        wordPart = searchWord.substr(0, i);

      }

  }

  search(q) {
    const query = SearchIndexManager.cleanSearchText(q);
    const queryWords = query.split(' ');
    let foundObjs = false;
    let newFoundObjs;
    let i;
    let j;
    let searchText;
    let found;

    for (i = 0; i < queryWords.length; i += 1) {
      newFoundObjs = this.shortIndexes[queryWords[i].substr(0, 3)];

      if (!newFoundObjs) {
        foundObjs = [];
        break;
      }

      if (foundObjs === false || foundObjs.length > newFoundObjs.length) {
        foundObjs = newFoundObjs;
      }
    }

    newFoundObjs = {};

    for (j = 0; j < foundObjs.length; j += 1) {
      found = true;
      searchText = this.fullTexts[foundObjs[j]];

      for (i = 0; i < queryWords.length; i += 1) {
        if (searchText.indexOf(queryWords[i]) === -1) {
          found = false;
          break;
        }
      }

      if (found) {
        newFoundObjs[foundObjs[j]] = true;
      }
    }

    return newFoundObjs;
  }

const badCharsRe = /[`~!@#$%^&*()\-_=+\[\]\\|{}'";:\/?.>,<\s]+/g;
const trimRe = /^\s+|\s$/g;

// full text search for js
export default class SearchIndexManager {
  constructor() {
    this.shortIndexes = {};
    this.fullTexts = {};
  }

  static cleanSearchText(text) {
    let result = text;
    const hasTag = result.charAt(0) === '%';
    result = result.replace(badCharsRe, ' ').replace(trimRe, '');
    result = result.replace(/[^A-Za-z0-9]/g, ch => {
      const latinizeCh = LatinizeMap[ch];
      return latinizeCh !== undefined ? latinizeCh : ch;
    });
    result = result.toLowerCase();
    if (hasTag) {
      result = `%$ result}`;
    }

    return result;
  }

  indexObject(id, objectString) {
    if (this.fullTexts[id] !== undefined) {
      return false;
    }

    const searchText = SearchIndexManager.cleanSearchText(objectString);

    if (!searchText.length) {
      return false;
    }

    this.fullTexts[id] = searchText;

    searchText.split(' ').forEach(searchWord => {
      const len = Math.min(searchWord.length, 3);
      let wordPart;
      let i;
      for (i = 1; i <= len; i += 1) {
        wordPart = searchWord.substr(0, i);
        if (this.shortIndexes[wordPart] === undefined) {
          this.shortIndexes[wordPart] = [id];
        } else {
          this.shortIndexes[wordPart].push(id);
        }
      }
    });
    return true;
  }

  search(q) {
    const query = SearchIndexManager.cleanSearchText(q);

    const queryWords = query.split(' ');
    let foundObjs = false;
    let newFoundObjs;
    let i;
    let j;
    let searchText;
    let found;

    for (i = 0; i < queryWords.length; i += 1) {
      newFoundObjs = this.shortIndexes[queryWords[i].substr(0, 3)];
      if (!newFoundObjs) {
        foundObjs = [];
        break;
      }
      if (foundObjs === false || foundObjs.length > newFoundObjs.length) {
        foundObjs = newFoundObjs;
      }
    }

    newFoundObjs = {};

    for (j = 0; j < foundObjs.length; j += 1) {
      found = true;
      searchText = this.fullTexts[foundObjs[j]];
      for (i = 0; i < queryWords.length; i += 1) {
        if (searchText.indexOf(queryWords[i]) === -1) {
          found = false;
          break;
        }
      }
      if (found) {
        newFoundObjs[foundObjs[j]] = true;
      }
    }

    return newFoundObjs;
  }
}
